  "methods": "<p>Metagenome datasets, filtered sequencing reads following the standard operating procedure of the DOE-JGI Metagenome Annotation Pipeline (Huntemann et al. 2016) were analyzed for tetranucleotide counts with KMC (version 3.1.1) (Kokot, Długosz, and Deorowicz 2017). Tetranucleotide counts were converted into frequencies (e.g. 4-mer count divided by the total count of all 4-mers) and ratios of frequencies (e.g. 4-mer frequencies divided by all other permutations of 4-mer frequencies).</p>",
